# ClinicHub — Multi-Clinic Management Platform

Full-stack BI platform for clinic management with automated 
Jane App data import, financial analytics, and forecasting.

## Tech Stack
- Backend: FastAPI, PostgreSQL, SQLAlchemy
- Frontend: React, Recharts
- Testing: pytest

## Features
- JWT authentication with role-based access
- ETL pipeline importing 700+ patients, 2000+ sessions from CSV
- FIFO payment allocation engine
- Real-time financial dashboards & forecasting
- Device ROI tracking

